Method Detail

runFunction

public boolean runFunction(String[] parameters)
Run the Function of a FunctionModule

Parameters:
parameters - array of String containing the parameters.
parameters[0] argument is always the method name.
If null is used as parameters it sends the allowed parameters list to the XTTProperties.printFail(java.lang.String) method and returns.
Returns:
boolean containing true when the method was executed and false if not.

dumpFunctions

public void dumpFunctions()
Dump the Functions of a FunctionModule. Iterates over all Functions of the FunctionModule and calls it with a null parameter.
